No one in my group of friends has got fat for this exact reason. Every now and then one of us starts to put on the pounds and the others will mercilessly rip on him until they lose the weight. We're all really close so it never feels mean-hearted and it honestly works. One obese guy joined the group and he's already run a marathon and is now one of the healthiest of us.
Not for everyone I know but it works for us. Except Gareth... Gareth is still a bit fat.
